title: Nazi Underworld - Season 1 & 2
description:
Nazi Underworld - Season 1 & 2

This series provides a surprising look at the world of Adolf Hitler and the Third Reich. Each episode tackles a different mystery; from the secret missions of the Second World War, to the truth about the Nazi gold hidden in the Alps, to revealing insights about Hitler himself - was he bipolar? Did he use cocaine?

Season 1

Ep 1 - Hitler's Henchman
Ep 2 - Hitler's Desert Fox
Ep 3 - Hitler's Women
Ep 4 - Hitler's Architect
Ep 5 - Hitler's Money
Ep 6 - Hitler's Family

Season 2

Ep 1 - The Hess Enigma
Ep 2 - Patient Hitler
Ep 3 - The Ghost Of U-513
Ep 4 - Nazi Gold
Ep 5 - Deadly Missions
